OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1780625006
OL,3,CSwinney to chair meeting on evacuated
OL,4,Cformer mining village
OL,6,FThe First Minister is to visit a
OL,7,FClackmannanshire village that was
OL,8,Fevacuated last month over ground
OL,9,Fmovement.
OL,11,FOn Friday, John Swinney will visit
OL,12,FCoalsnaughton, a former mining village
OL,13,Fwhere residents began to be evacuated
OL,14,Fon May 18 amid an investigation into
OL,15,Fthe ground movement.
OL,17,FResidents across around 100 homes were
OL,18,Ftold on Wednesday they would need to
OL,19,Fspend eight more weeks out of their
OL,20,Fhomes before the cause of the issue
OL,21,Fcan be established.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
