PN,30802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1780625006
OL,3,CSwinney to chair meeting on evacuated
OL,4,Cformer mining village
OL,6,FBrian Leishman, Labour MP for Alloa
OL,7,Fand Grangemouth, raised the issue at
OL,8,FPrime Minister's Questions ` saying
OL,9,Fpeople in Coalsnaughton are suffering
OL,10,F"emotional and financial distress".
OL,12,FMr Swinney is expected to chair a
OL,13,Fround table with members of the local
OL,14,Fcouncil, the Mining Remediation
OL,15,FAuthority and other organisations.
OL,17,FHe will be joined by Justice Secretary
OL,18,FNeil Gray.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
