CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1780625006
OL,3,CSwinney to chair meeting on evacuated
OL,4,Cformer mining village
OL,6,FAhead of the visit on Friday, the
OL,7,FFirst Minister said: "This is a very
OL,8,Fdistressing situation for the
OL,9,Fresidents of Coalsnaughton who have
OL,10,Fhad to leave their homes with no clear
OL,11,Findication of when they might be able
OL,12,Fto return.
OL,14,F"I understand the urgency of resolving
OL,15,Fthis issue at the earliest possible
OL,16,Fopportunity so people can get their
OL,17,Flives back on track, and I welcome the
OL,18,Fopportunity to hear about the work
OL,19,Fbeing done to support them.
OL,26,@oD@VOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1780625006
OL,3,CSwinney to chair meeting on evacuated
OL,4,Cformer mining village
OL,6,F"Whilst it is necessary that the
OL,7,FMining Remediation Authority carries
OL,8,Fout safety investigations, people are
OL,9,Funderstandably concerned about the
OL,10,Flength of time this might take.
OL,12,F"It is absolutely critical that they
OL,13,Fare provided with clear communication
OL,14,Fand further clarity as soon as
OL,15,Fpossible on what will happen in the
OL,16,Fcoming weeks.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1780625006
OL,3,CSwinney to chair meeting on evacuated
OL,4,Cformer mining village
OL,6,FHe added: "Given the UK Government has
OL,7,Fresponsibility for the Authority, the
OL,8,FJustice Secretary Neil Gray has also
OL,9,Fwritten to the UK Energy Secretary to
OL,10,Fensure he is doing everything possible
OL,11,Fto see that investigations are carried
OL,12,Fout as quickly as possible.
OL,14,F"The Scottish Government will continue
OL,15,Fto meet regularly with
OL,16,FClackmannanshire Council to provide
OL,17,Fsupport where and when it is required."
OL,19,FMr Gray previously said: "This
OL,20,Fcontinues to be a very distressing
OL,21,Fsituation for the residents.
OL,26,@nD@KOUvD@AOUyD@gO]{D@ZOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1780625006
OL,3,CSwinney to chair meeting on evacuated
OL,4,Cformer mining village
OL,6,F"I have expressed to the Mining
OL,7,FRemediation Authority my significant
OL,8,Fconcern that its investigations will
OL,9,Ftake at least another eight weeks to
OL,10,Ffind the source of the ground
OL,11,Fmovement, due to the impact this will
OL,12,Fhave on so many households.
OL,14,F"The MRA's decision is absolutely
OL,15,Fcritical to plot the route forward for
OL,16,Fthe residents so I made clear to them
OL,17,Fthat they have an absolute
OL,18,Fresponsibility and moral obligation to
OL,19,Ftake this decision as quickly as
OL,20,Fpossible.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1780625006
OL,3,CSwinney to chair meeting on evacuated
OL,4,Cformer mining village
OL,6,F"Given the MRA is a public body under
OL,7,FUK Government control, I have written
OL,8,Fto the UK Energy Secretary to ensure
OL,9,Fhe is taking all possible actions to
OL,10,Fensure the investigations are being
OL,11,Fcarried out as quickly as possible.
OL,13,F"The Scottish Government continues to
OL,14,Fregularly meet with Clackmannanshire
OL,15,FCouncil to provide support where it is
OL,16,Frequired."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUxD@JO]
